channel.title: Portforwarding | CanYouSeeMe.org
channel.description:
Ok so, I have a server and I have made loads before but I had help from people and yes they spoon fed me but I tried my best to learn, I have tried to portforward and I am sure it is done right but I am not sure, my friends can't connect to the server when it is online, the IP's are all right but for some reason they can't connect, it says that they can't connect. Can you help me please? I have teamviewer aswell.
CanYouSeeMe.org: I use this and check the ports I use for the server, they should be on 43594 or 43595 or 55555 but it says error connection timed out or something, someone please help me.
P.S I use uTorrent aswell.
